flowchart TD
  R[Request - UI action] --> SA[Server Action]
  SA --> CP{checkPermission<br/>module/action<br/>organization/vertical}
  CP -- allowed --> ACT[Perform action]
  ACT --> DB[(Prisma<br/>MySQL)]
  ACT --> LOG[ActivityLog<br/>audit trail]
  ACT --> OPT[Notify or email<br/>Pusher real-time]
  CP -- denied --> DENY[Access Denied<br/>error response]
